Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.78,0:00:06.12,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.26,0:00:07.99,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,That's the last of it, Filthy Rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.23,0:00:10.34,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Just Rich, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.47,0:00:13.40,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,And on behalf of Riches' Barnyard Bargains,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.49,0:00:16.95,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,thanks for another season shipment of Zap Apple Jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.46,0:00:18.28,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Our pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:19.24,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,See you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.59,0:00:27.88,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom, did you pack up the cider into the same crates as the Zap Apple Jam?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.20,0:00:29.01,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Sure did!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:30.42,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Now that I'm getting older,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.50,0:00:33.84,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I wanna prove that I can handle more responsibility on the farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.07,0:00:35.81,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,But the crates aren't marked!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.97,0:00:38.68,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You kept track of what went into which crate, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:41.97,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.97,0:00:43.81,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I totally kept track of everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.71,0:00:45.11,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.51,0:00:48.45,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Because we wouldn't want Filthy Rich to get a shipment of cider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.45,0:00:50.63,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,when he's supposed to get Zap Apple Jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.76,0:00:54.58,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You know how Granny feels about selling cider anywhere, but on the farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.00,0:00:57.12,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Are you sure he got the right crates?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.20,0:00:59.36,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Sure I'm sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:04.37,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Now, why don't you and Big Mac head on out to the house and let me finish up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.69,0:01:09.25,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,If you gave Rich the Zap Apple Jam,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.38,0:01:10.69,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,then what's this here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.52,0:01:13.34,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Extra?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.83,0:01:14.96,BigMac,,0,0,0,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.02,0:01:58.41,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Granny knows, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.49,0:02:01.98,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,I wasn't trying to make off with the shipment of cider, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:04.31,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Because I would never do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.59,0:02:05.65,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.65,0:02:08.81,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,We know exactly whose fault it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.55,0:02:16.91,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Now, why in tarnation would you lie to me, Apple Bloom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.91,0:02:20.67,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I was kinda hoping I could fix it before anypony found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.67,0:02:24.49,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Telling lies won't fix anything. Trust me. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:26.43,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,How could you possibly know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.43,0:02:28.89,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,You've never told a lie in your whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.81,0:02:36.96,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.23,0:02:38.76,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Oh, sugarcube.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:42.51,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Your big sister lied so much when she was a filly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:44.76,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,The whole family ended up in a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.27,0:02:46.18,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.41,0:02:47.59,BigMac,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.53,0:02:51.05,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You might as well tell her the whole story.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.05,0:02:53.21,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,It might even do her some good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.21,0:02:58.41,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,When Applejack and Big Mac were just a wittle older than you are now,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.41,0:03:02.75,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,they both kept a squabbling over who would run the farm better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:07.71,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,All I'm sayin' is that you may have plenty of brawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.71,0:03:11.27,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,but I'm the one with the ideas on how to run things better around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:14.17,BigMac,,0,0,0,,Applejack, Applejack, Applejack,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:18.13,BigMac,,0,0,0,,ideas are all well and good, but you can't plow a field with 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:21.09,BigMac,,0,0,0,,I don't know how many times I've told you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:22.11,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Too many!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.11,0:03:26.23,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,You two horned toads better stop jabberin' and get to workin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.23,0:03:27.25,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they'd better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:28.99,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,I need you to go to town.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.99,0:03:30.77,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,The apple blight's been awful
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:35.51,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,and if we don't get more spray, cider season'll be shorter than a dwarf crabapple tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.26,0:03:38.73,BigMac,,0,0,0,,It's like I was just tellin' Cousin Braeburn last week,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:41.97,BigMac,,0,0,0,,now there's a pony who knows how to put his back into a problem…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:46.25,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Hi there, Filthy Rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:47.70,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Just Rich, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:51.54,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,And I'd like you to meet my fiancée, Spoiled Milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:54.31,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Honey, this is Applejack and Big Mac.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:57.69,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,The two hardest working ponies at Sweet Apple Acres.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:04:02.99,SpoiledRich,,0,0,0,,You work on a farm? How quaint.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:05.29,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Now, dear, be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.29,0:04:07.75,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Sweet Apple Acres makes Zap Apple Jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.75,0:04:09.75,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,It's one of dad's best-sellers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.53,0:04:13.29,SpoiledRich,,0,0,0,,You mean one of your best-sellers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:16.99,SpoiledRich,,0,0,0,,My amazing husband-to-be is running the Rich family business now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:19.89,SpoiledRich,,0,0,0,,Did you know that? Well, now you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:22.27,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Oh, my Spoiled Milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:24.05,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,She's just proud of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.05,0:04:27.23,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,But she's right. I'm in charge of the store now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:30.49,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,And I'm just burstin' with ideas I wanna try.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:31.61,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.61,0:04:33.51,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Well, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.51,0:04:35.77,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Cider season's around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:38.13,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Why not let me sell it for ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:40.75,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,That is an interesting idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:43.65,BigMac,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe it's interesting and maybe it ain't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:45.89,BigMac,,0,0,0,,But it's definitely not a new idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:48.35,BigMac,,0,0,0,,Granny Smith told us your grandpa, Stinkin' Rich,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:51.91,BigMac,,0,0,0,,used to ask her every year if he could sell our cider in your store.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:54.21,BigMac,,0,0,0,,And Granny told him every year about the tradition
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:57.65,BigMac,,0,0,0,,of everypony in Ponyville linin' up out at Sweet Apple Acres.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:59.90,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,So start a new tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:02.41,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Some day, one of y'all take over the farm
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:05.03,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,just like I've taken over the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:09.11,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,I'm guessin' it'll be the one with the best ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.11,0:05:12.49,BigMac,,0,0,0,,Well, now, as I've said many a time before,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:14.07,BigMac,,0,0,0,,ideas are all well and good,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.07,0:05:15.51,BigMac,,0,0,0,,But you can't plow a field…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.51,0:05:16.49,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.49,0:05:19.65,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,How 'bout we give you three barrels of cider early?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:22.41,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And if it sells well, we'll make a deal for the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.85,0:05:24.83,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Hey, now! Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.83,0:05:28.21,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Come on, honey. I've gotta get everything ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.17,0:05:30.35,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I tell ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:33.43,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,If the future means me runnin' Sweet Apple Acres
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.43,0:05:36.47,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,and you bein' quiet, I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:45.03,BigMac,,0,0,0,,I just can't believe you'd make a deal with Filthy Rich without even talkin' to Granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:46.57,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Granny will love the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:49.95,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And then she'll decide that I'm the one who should take over the farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:50.75,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:52.20,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,See what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.97,0:05:56.55,BigMac,,0,0,0,,Applejack here had another one of her big ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.55,0:05:59.07,BigMac,,0,0,0,,And I think we all know my position on ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.07,0:05:59.67,BigMac,,0,0,0,,You ca…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:01.99,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Can't plow a field with 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:01.99,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Can't plow a field with 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.99,0:06:03.84,BigMac,,0,0,0,,Ee…Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:06.17,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Big idea, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.77,0:06:10.09,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Actually, more of an opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:12.39,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You see, we ran into Filthy Rich in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:14.51,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Did you know he's runnin' the family store now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.51,0:06:19.23,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,And what does this here… opportunity mean for Sweet Apple Acres?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:22.71,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, since cider season is almost here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:27.99,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,he — or, I mean, I thought it'd be a good idea to give him a few barrels of cider
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:30.37,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,to sell at the store before the season starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.97,0:06:32.58,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.89,0:06:36.08,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.95,0:06:42.37,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,But Granny!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.37,0:06:46.27,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Why can't we sell a few barrels of cider early to Filthy Rich?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.27,0:06:50.95,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And how is it any different than when you gave Zap Apple Jam to Filthy's grandpappy to sell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.95,0:06:54.67,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Your cider and your jam ain't the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.67,0:06:57.53,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Zap apple jam jars preserve the flavor for moons,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:07:01.63,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,but cider starts to spoil the second it comes out the press.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:03.85,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,That is why every cider season,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.85,0:07:06.91,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,all of ponyville lines up at Sweet Apple Acres.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:09.03,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,And first come is first served. Hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:11.29,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I get what you're sayin', Granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:14.71,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,But couldn't you make an exception just this once?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.71,0:07:16.79,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I sort of promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:22.31,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Besides, cider makin' is iffy business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:24.81,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,And we're probably not goin' to have a lot this year anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:26.17,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,what with all the blight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:28.17,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,I am sorry, Applejack,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:30.95,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,but you's just gonna have to unpromise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:37.29,BigMac,,0,0,0,,I hate to say I told you so, Applejack, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:40.89,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You and I both know you don't hate to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:43.79,BigMac,,0,0,0,,Well, I've always thought that the most important thing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:46.07,BigMac,,0,0,0,,a pony can do is say exactly what's on his mind
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:47.29,BigMac,,0,0,0,,to anypony who'll listen,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:49.43,BigMac,,0,0,0,,so everypony everywhere always knows
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.43,0:07:50.93,BigMac,,0,0,0,,everything you're thinkin'. And…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.93,0:07:54.09,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And you don't ever have to listen to anypony else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:07:55.15,BigMac,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.77,0:07:56.80,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:02.62,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Well, if it ain't my new business partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.82,0:08:05.39,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,About the cider, Rich…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:09.12,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Take a look at what I did last night after we made our deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.98,0:08:13.02,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Pretty great, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:14.45,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,The thing is…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:16.55,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I don't think I can get you any.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:17.79,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:18.51,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:21.49,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,I did all this work on your say-so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.49,0:08:23.35,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,We shook hooves and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:25.31,BigMac,,0,0,0,,Well, you see, at Sweet Apple Acres,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:26.98,BigMac,,0,0,0,,we've always been about quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:29.01,BigMac,,0,0,0,,And while your basic jam jar'll keep…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:32.19,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Plus it's been a tough harvest this year, what with all the blight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:36.08,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Sounds to me like you're trying to make excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:38.85,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Whenever granddad dealt with Granny Smith,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:40.41,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,she kept her word!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.73,0:08:43.39,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,If you can't do that, then maybe our families
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.39,0:08:45.34,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,should stop doing business together,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:46.61,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,altogether!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:50.60,BigMac,,0,0,0,,Now, now, the thing is, Rich,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:52.45,BigMac,,0,0,0,,it ain't really up to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.45,0:08:54.05,BigMac,,0,0,0,,You see, Granny's…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:54.72,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:56.87,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Wait. Granny's sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:08:58.53,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:08:59.80,BigMac,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:01.19,BigMac,,0,0,0,,Nopony did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:03.71,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What Big Mac means is…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:05.94,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,We've been trying to keep it quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:07.82,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Don't want people to make rash decisions
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.82,0:09:09.66,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,about doing business with Sweet Apple Acres
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.66,0:09:12.56,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,just because we're… a little short-hooved at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:13.61,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:15.35,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Of course, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.35,0:09:17.36,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,I am so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:20.78,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Please let me know if there's anything I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:22.50,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Much appreciated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:23.90,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,But right now, we…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.90,0:09:25.90,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,We only ask for your understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:27.71,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,during this difficult time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:32.80,BigMac,,0,0,0,,You were supposed to tell Rich the simple truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:36.07,BigMac,,0,0,0,,But instead, you made things worse with a giant lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:38.33,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,W-w-what was I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:39.65,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You heard Rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.65,0:09:40.96,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,If I told him the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:43.56,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,he was gonna stop doing business with us altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:45.83,BigMac,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but that's only because…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.83,0:09:48.72,BigMac,,0,0,0,,I forgot to ask if we had any oat crumbles
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.72,0:09:50.94,BigMac,,0,0,0,,for this delicious-looking salad, Granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:53.64,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll go take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.49,0:09:58.18,BigMac,,0,0,0,,That was only because you made promises you couldn't keep!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:10:03.06,BigMac,,0,0,0,,But there's gotta be a better way out of this mess than by making up some story about Granny being sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:04.54,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, it worked, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.47,0:10:08.74,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Sorry to drop by unannounced.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.82,0:10:11.14,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,We just wanted to come by to wish Granny
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:12.63,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,a speedy recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:14.00,BigMac,,0,0,0,,Look, sis,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:16.65,BigMac,,0,0,0,,our good friend Mr. Rich and his fiancee…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:17.59,BigMac,,0,0,0,,are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.83,0:10:19.93,BigMac,,0,0,0,,Oh, and they brought flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:21.23,BigMac,,0,0,0,,For Granny!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:23.53,BigMac,,0,0,0,,On account that she is sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.61,0:10:24.92,BigMac,,0,0,0,,Like you said!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:26.64,BigMac,,0,0,0,,Ain't that sweet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.38,0:10:29.63,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Excuse me one second!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:34.98,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,What in tarnation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.12,0:10:36.36,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry, Granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:37.88,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I… I didn't see you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:41.53,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Ya came blastin' in so fast, t'weren't possible to see nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.34,0:10:43.89,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Can you go out to the barn?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.89,0:10:45.57,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I… I think I might have left a…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.57,0:10:47.14,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,blight sprayer in the orchard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:49.85,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Are you outta your apple-picking mind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:51.92,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,It's supper time, girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:52.85,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I know, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.85,0:10:55.90,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,if we forgot a sprayer, I'd wanna get it before dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:57.10,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You go start counting…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.10,0:10:59.08,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,and I'll tell Big Mac we'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:10:59.93,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:04.94,BigMac,,0,0,0,,So from that moment on, I took on to referring to myself as…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:06.93,BigMac,,0,0,0,,Big or Large or…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.05,0:11:08.79,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Oh, Applejack!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:12.65,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Your brother was just explaining why he always wears his yoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:16.61,SpoiledRich,,0,0,0,,Even though we asked him how your grandmare is doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.81,0:11:19.14,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, you know how Big Mac can get to…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.14,0:11:21.57,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,to talking, especially when he's upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:25.19,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And right now he's just as worried about Granny Smith as I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.11,0:11:27.83,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:29.81,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Is she doing that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:32.26,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, one thing's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.26,0:11:34.75,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,She… she shouldn't be seeing anypony right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:39.77,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,In fact, I'm getting more upset just thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.77,0:11:40.76,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.73,0:11:46.78,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,What in the frilly fumidil has gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.00,0:11:47.93,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.05,0:11:51.52,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I just decided if I helped you, it would go faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.75,0:11:52.92,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Well, you're too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.92,0:11:54.73,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,All the sprayers are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:11:58.37,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:00.58,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Say, Granny,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.79,0:12:03.63,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,when did you first fight the apple blight again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.78,0:12:07.88,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,It was my second year here in Ponyville…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.07,0:12:12.47,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,They was before I had the rick on the one knee…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.73,0:12:16.67,BigMac,,0,0,0,,And others say that's how the trees got to growing so tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:17.33,BigMac,,0,0,0,,But to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:19.67,BigMac,,0,0,0,,it's just how I got my cutie mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:23.73,SpoiledRich,,0,0,0,,But we asked when we could come back to see Granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:26.13,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Big Mac didn't want to be rude,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.13,0:12:29.21,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,but you just can't see Granny right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:30.31,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,because she is…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.51,0:12:32.69,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Got apple blight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:36.31,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,I thought only trees got the blight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.57,0:12:39.28,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's usually the case…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.15,0:12:43.75,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,The doctors think it's from working in the orchard for so many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.46,0:12:49.06,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You see, we had to take Granny to Ponyville General.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:51.54,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,We just got back right before you showed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:52.93,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.09,0:12:54.47,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,That is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.38,0:12:57.77,SpoiledRich,,0,0,0,,It's not contagious, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:00.25,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll be fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:01.47,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,but you should leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.29,0:13:03.21,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:05.93,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.02,0:13:08.29,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,We gonna have to hurry if we wanna get there
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.29,0:13:10.47,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,before visiting hours are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:11.70,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:13.25,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Wait! Get where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:15.64,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Why, the hospital, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.97,0:13:17.75,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we'll see you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:25.95,BigMac,,0,0,0,,Telling Filthy Rich that Granny is in the hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:27.95,BigMac,,0,0,0,,just made everything one hundred times worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.21,0:13:29.91,BigMac,,0,0,0,,What are we supposed to do now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.21,0:13:32.05,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.88,0:13:35.79,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Got my second-best teeth right in the pig pen,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:38.46,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,and that was the worst case of apple blight
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:40.33,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,I have yet ever seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:42.00,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I'd love to hear more, Granny,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:44.21,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,but we gotta get to the hospital right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.45,0:13:45.44,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,The hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.57,0:13:47.34,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Why? Who's sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:49.05,BigMac,,0,0,0,,You are, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:53.04,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What he means is, you're needed at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:55.05,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Whatever for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.61,0:13:57.73,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,It's the apple blight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.93,0:13:59.71,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,It's starting to infect ponies now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:02.23,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,The doctors need an expert opinion, and
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:05.63,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,nopony knows more about fighting blight than Granny Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:08.82,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Well, what in tarnation are we waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:09.87,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.05,0:14:20.36,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You know, we're supposed to go in…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.61,0:14:21.45,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,in the back…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:25.26,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,To avoid anypony in the waiting room with the blight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.17,0:14:30.77,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Oops, I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:35.25,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,This is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:38.04,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And now you don't have to worry about catching the blight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:39.83,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,If you say so, deary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:41.25,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Now you wait right here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:41.95,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,while I…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:44.24,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,check on your presentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.81,0:14:47.49,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,What in the rotten rhubarb is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.13,0:14:51.14,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Fancy meeting you two here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:53.73,SpoiledRich,,0,0,0,,Well, we told you we were coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:56.03,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,I'm glad we found you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.03,0:14:58.78,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,because I can't seem to find Granny's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.01,0:15:03.00,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Or any nurses who've even heard about a pony with apple blight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.24,0:15:04.05,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Granny's room…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:04.84,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.02,0:15:06.00,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,just go down here,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.53,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,take a left, then a right,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:08.42,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,go down some stairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:09.84,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,up a bunch more stairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:10.88,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,through the cafeteria,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:11.75,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,left three more times,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.75,0:15:12.72,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,and then you're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.88,0:15:14.52,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Easy as Granny's apple pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.96,0:15:18.45,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Aren't you coming with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:19.52,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I'll catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:21.20,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I gotta find Big Mac.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:23.91,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Okay, Granny,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.91,0:15:26.32,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,just wait here one second, and we can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.89,0:15:28.32,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Where are you two going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.37,0:15:29.57,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Big Mac can't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:30.17,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,He…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.44,0:15:31.72,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,might be contagious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.96,0:15:33.47,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Contagious?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.96,0:15:33.47,BigMac,,0,0,0,,Contagious?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:38.61,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,All right, climb up here, and I'll cover you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.61,0:15:40.81,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Then I'll bring Rich in, tell him you're Granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.81,0:15:42.53,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,But you're not allowed to take the sheets off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.53,0:15:45.02,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You moan a few times, he leaves, and this whole thing is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:47.92,BigMac,,0,0,0,,This is spinning way out of control, Applejack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.25,0:15:51.61,BigMac,,0,0,0,,Now, I know you thought sellin' cider in Filthy's store was a good idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:54.76,BigMac,,0,0,0,,but it ain't worth lying to him about Granny being sick
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:56.29,BigMac,,0,0,0,,and needing to go to the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.55,0:15:59.32,BigMac,,0,0,0,,or fibbing to Granny about them wantin' her to come here
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.32,0:16:00.69,BigMac,,0,0,0,,to talk about the blight, or…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:04.27,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Big Macintosh, please, just listen to me for once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:06.59,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,This ain't about my ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:08.65,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,If Rich finds out about all the lies,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:11.20,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,he'll cut off ties with us, and the farm will go under.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:14.49,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Now do you want that to happen or do you wanna help?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:15.89,BigMac,,0,0,0,,Why can't you be Granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:18.09,BigMac,,0,0,0,,You're her size and this is all your fault in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.09,0:16:20.76,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I would, but if I let you do the talkin',
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.76,0:16:23.50,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,you'd just ramble on and on until we all got caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.91,0:16:27.89,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Just lay down, keep still
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:31.09,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,and promise me you won't say anything, for once in your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:32.57,BigMac,,0,0,0,,Eeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:37.05,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Granny!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:40.60,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Granny!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.53,0:16:44.45,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,It's about time! What is goin' on around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.45,0:16:47.03,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Uh, Granny, they need you to wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.03,0:16:48.51,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I-I'll come get ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.51,0:16:49.29,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:51.57,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.67,0:16:55.14,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,We've been going in circles looking for Granny's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:58.45,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, you're in luck 'cause it's — it's right over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:17:01.37,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And this time, I'll make sure you don't get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:08.09,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What in the dadgum…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:10.13,SpoiledRich,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:13.30,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,He… I mean, she was right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.94,0:17:15.88,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. We gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.62,0:17:20.15,SpoiledRich,,0,0,0,,I-is that Granny Smith?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:22.18,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Where are they taking her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.63,0:17:26.50,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You two, don't lose that gurney.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:29.05,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Granny, what are you doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.05,0:17:30.89,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You were supposed to stay there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.89,0:17:33.10,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,It was a supply closet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.27,0:17:37.45,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, okay, come with me, but be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:40.95,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You know, save your voice for the big presentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:05.52,SomeponyYellow,,0,0,0,,I-I-I'm sorry, but you can't get any closer without a gown and mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.52,0:18:08.77,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,But — but — but — but that's my brother on there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:11.84,SomeponyYellow,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. This is our best doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.84,0:18:15.02,SomeponyYellow,,0,0,0,,She'll have your brother back on his hooves in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:21.74,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Now apple blight is a serious disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:25.46,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Did she say apple blight?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.46,0:18:28.25,SomeponyLightPink,,0,0,0,,I-I think she said gasket mites.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:31.87,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,And once your trunk turns red like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.87,0:18:35.14,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,the only thing to do is prune the branches.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:37.66,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Granny!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:42.10,SomeponyLightPink,,0,0,0,,Did you say "prune them branches"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:42.92,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Well, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.92,0:18:46.32,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,What else you gonna do once the blight gets this bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:58.40,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Everypony, just stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:19:01.32,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,This is all a big misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.54,0:19:04.19,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's a big lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.59,0:19:08.88,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Big Mac?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.32,0:19:10.67,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Granny Smith?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:13.46,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,What is going on here, Applejack?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.78,0:19:16.30,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,That is a darn good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.58,0:19:22.85,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if I was worried that nopony was listenin' to my ideas
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.85,0:19:25.81,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,or just nervous that I wouldn't be the one to end up runnin' the farm,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:29.83,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,but I promised somethin' to Filthy Rich that I couldn't deliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.83,0:19:32.44,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And I was too embarrassed to admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.66,0:19:34.82,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,So Granny was never sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:38.07,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,And there ain't no apple-blighted ponies?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:39.59,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:42.15,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Those were all lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.15,0:19:44.02,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,A-and I thought if you found out,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:46.40,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,you'd stop doin' business with the farm,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:49.08,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,So I just kept tellin' more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:51.16,SomeponyYellow,,0,0,0,,So she's not a doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:54.89,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Please don't make Granny and the farm suffer for what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.89,0:19:57.17,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,This whole thing is my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.17,0:19:59.20,BigMac,,0,0,0,,That's not entirely true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:02.59,BigMac,,0,0,0,,Maybe if I paid more attention to what you had to say
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.59,0:20:04.26,BigMac,,0,0,0,,instead of talkin' all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:06.55,BigMac,,0,0,0,,none of this would have happened in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:09.89,BigMac,,0,0,0,,I just need to talk less, listen more,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.45,0:20:11.87,BigMac,,0,0,0,,And especially to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.71,0:20:14.15,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Thanks, big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:17.42,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And whether it's me runnin' Sweet Apple Acres or you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:19.81,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I know it'll be in good hooves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.29,0:20:21.19,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Well, that's nice,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:23.73,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,but I don't know what in blazes you two are talkin' about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:26.21,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,I ain't goin' anywhere anytime soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:27.71,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Runnin' the farm…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.71,0:20:29.60,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Not after this display,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:30.79,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,not likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:34.52,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,And don't you go gettin' any ideas
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.52,0:20:37.09,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,about cuttin' ties with Sweet Apple Acres,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.09,0:20:40.28,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Or I'm goin' right to your grandpappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.28,0:20:41.13,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Get me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.43,0:20:43.22,FilthyRich,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.56,0:20:48.18,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Now who here still wants to hear about the apple blight?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.00,0:20:51.16,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Now, when I was a filly…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.50,0:20:54.53,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you told all those lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.53,0:20:57.04,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,It's not a story I'm proud of,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:21:00.77,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,but it taught me a lifelong lesson about bein' honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.77,0:21:03.15,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I hope you learned somethin', too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:04.67,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I sure did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.67,0:21:07.30,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I learned that nopony starts out perfect,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.30,0:21:11.12,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,and sometimes you gotta make a few mistakes to figure out who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:12.37,BigMac,,0,0,0,,Eeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.54,0:21:17.08,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,But I think the most important thing I learned is who really runs Sweet Apple Acres.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.49,0:21:18.72,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.89,0:21:19.98,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,You're darn tootin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:23.73,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Now, everypony, quit your lollygaggery and get back to work…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.73,0:21:27.68,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Right after we have a glass of cider.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:35.10,Somepony,,0,0,0,,SCHASTLIVY PONEC
